org.zamia.instgraph.synth.model

Class IGSMExprEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zamia.instgraph.synth.model.IGSMExprEngine

  • public class IGSMExprEngine
extends java.lang.Object
    The expression engine - a singleton factory (not abstract since there is only one implementation) Lets the use create ExprNode trees easily and efficiently, yet will automatically seperate out all boolean expression parts and represent them as BDDs. Reason for that is that we need to answer questions of tautology or contradiction efficiently and some logic optimization is nice to have here as well. All expression node trees produced by this factory are immutable.
    Author:
    Guenter Bartsch
